  "body": "#### This resource pack improves the enchanted glint on tools with a <span style=\"color:#b96ad9\"><strong>glowing effect</strong>,</span> giving them a more vibrant and stylish look.\n\n![Sinnelar - Enchantment Glows Minecraft Resource Pack Showcase with Hold My Items Mod](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Sinnelar/sinnelar-assets/heads/main/enchantment-glows/showcases/enchantment-glows-with-hold-my-items-mod.webp)\n\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Sinnelar/sinnelar-assets/heads/main/enchantment-glows/showcases/enchantment-glows-bow.gif\" alt=\"Minecraft Enchanted Bow Arrow Glowing Animation\" width=\"50%\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Sinnelar/sinnelar-assets/heads/main/enchantment-glows/showcases/enchantment-glows-crossbow.gif\" alt=\"Minecraft Enchanted Crossbow Arrow Glowing Animation\" width=\"50%\">\n<br>\n\nThis resource pack works fully in **<span style=\"color:#2dc26b\">Vanilla Minecraft 1.21.4 - 26.1</span>**\n\n**Enchanted Tools List:**\n- Swords\n- Axes\n- Pickaxes\n- Shovels\n- Hoes\n- Spears\n- Mace 3D\n- Bow\n- Crossbow\n- Fishing Rods\n- Trident (1.21.4+)\n- Shield (1.21.4+)\n\n**<span style=\"color:#e03e2d\">CIT Resewn required for versions below 1.21.4<br></span>**\n\n[**<span style=\"color:#e03e2d\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Sinnelar/sinnelar-assets/heads/main/enchantment-glows/ui/b-ct-d.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"177\" height=\"177\"></span>**](https://modrinth.com/mod/cit-resewn)\n\n**Credits:**\n- Yes, it's inspired by&nbsp;<strong>Actions & Stuff\n\n---\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://billing.sparkedhost.com/aff.php?aff=3122\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"sponsored noopener nofollow\">\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Sinnelar/sinnelar-assets/heads/main/sinnelar-affiliates/sparked-host-promo-code-2026-minecraft-sinnelar.webp\" alt=\"Sparked Host Promo Code 2026 - 25% OFF Minecraft Server Hosting with Code Sinnelar\" width=\"100%\">\n  </a>\n</div>",
